## ğŸ“Œ 2. Problem Statement

Managing large music libraries becomes difficult without a centralized system. Songs, artists, albums, and playlists often become scattered across folders. Manual management of audio files, cover images, and metadata leads to confusion and inefficiency.

**TuneHive solves this problem by providing:**

* A central admin dashboard
* Easy song uploads (audio + image)
* Playlist creation and assignment
* Real-time searching & filtering
* Cloud-based storage with AWS S3
* A modern UI for efficient content management

